# hellok8s-ci2  
Full CI/CD pipeline deploying a Flask application to a Kubernetes (Minikube) cluster using Jenkins, Docker, Terraform (infra), and Ansible.

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project demonstrates a complete DevOps workflow for deploying a containerized Flask microservice to Kubernetes through an automated CI/CD pipeline.  
The pipeline builds a Docker image, pushes it to DockerHub, and triggers an Ansible deployment that applies Kubernetes manifests to a Minikube cluster.  
This is a practical, end-to-end example of real DevOps automation.

